article_title: Private Payrolls Rose by 217,000 in November
article_text:
Private-sector payrolls increased more than expected in November, the most in five months and the latest indication of steady U.S. job growth.

Private payrolls in the U.S. rose by 217,000, said payroll processor Automatic Data Processing Inc. and...
